<li><a href="http://frc-pdr.readthedocs.io/en/latest/">FRC Programming Done Right</a> - Exhaustive and well-written guide to programming in FRC, the right way.</li>
<h2>Vision</h2>
<li><a href="https://github.com/wpilibsuite/cscore">CSCore</a><a data-role="trackawesomelist-badge" href="https://github.com/wpilibsuite/cscore" style="text-decoration:none;top: -2px;position: relative;margin-left:4px;margin-right:4px;font-weight:400;"><span style="color: #fff;font-size: 11px;font-family: Verdana, Geneva, DejaVu Sans,sans-serif;"><span style="padding:4px 4px 4px 6px;background: #555;border-top-left-radius: 4px;border-bottom-left-radius: 4px;">stars</span><span style="padding: 4px 6px 4px 4px;background: #007ec6;border-top-right-radius: 4px;border-bottom-right-radius: 4px;">24</span></span></a><!--TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_START____{"type":"repo","stargazerCount":24,"repo":"wpilibsuite/cscore"}____TRACK_AWESOME_REPO_ITEM_END--> - The CScore camera vision library from WPI.</li>
<li><a href="https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=rLwOkAJqImo">254 2016 Vision Talk</a> - The most complete lesson about vision tracking out there.</li>
<h2>Driving</h2>
